Adobe Creative Suite mastery (Photoshop, Illustrator, et al.);
Ability to self-manage multiple projects, deadlines and deliverables;
Experience with shipping software (preferably at a well-known software organization, either big or small);
BA/BFA in interactive design (or related design discipline) and/or 5+ years relevant experience.
